high_descs: Walk ahead to the wall and then veer right to get to the stove.
Pick the kettle up on the back burner of the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn around and veer right, back to the stove.
Place the kettle on the front right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean kettle on a stove.

put the kettle in the sink, fill the kettle with water, take the kettle
turn left, turn left, walk to the stove
put the kettle on the right front stove

high_descs: Go across the room to the stove.
Pick up the tea kettle on the front middle burner.
Turn, go past the island on the right, and take a right to the sink.
Wash the tea kettle in the sink.
Turn left and go back to the stove.
Set the cleaned tea kettle down on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned tea kettle on the stove.
